ersdictionaries.com/definition/academic/respond\" title=\" definition in Academic English\n \"><span class=\"xh\">respond</span></a> in the Oxford Learner's Dictionary of Academic English</span></span><div class=\"pron-link\">Check pronunciation:\n                        <a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/pronunciation/english/respond\">respond</a></div></div>\n","matches":[],"relatives":[],"nearBys":["resplendent adjective","resplendently adverb","respond verb","respondent noun","response noun"]},[]]